588
00:36:48,195 --> 00:36:49,780
Aku tak bercanda!

589
00:36:50,281 --> 00:36:52,491
Akan kujelaskan yang terjadi.

590
00:36:52,575 --> 00:36:54,160
Kau sudah tahu ini omong kosong.

591
00:36:54,243 --> 00:36:55,661
Tunggu, Eun-ho. Astaga, tunggu!

592
00:36:56,203 --> 00:36:58,414
Hei! Kumohon... Hentikan!

593
00:36:58,497 --> 00:36:59,707
Dia hamil!

594
00:37:01,751 --> 00:37:02,752
Hei!

595
00:37:08,340 --> 00:37:09,175
Satu pukulan saja.

596
00:37:10,176 --> 00:37:11,677
Biar kupukul sekali, Dong-min.

597
00:37:11,761 --> 00:37:12,636
Eun-ho!

598
00:37:12,720 --> 00:37:15,222
Beraninya kau bicara begitu padaku.

599
00:37:15,347 --> 00:37:17,850
Kau bukan adik kandung Dan-i.

600
00:37:17,933 --> 00:37:20,019
