601
00:37:21,812 --> 00:37:22,813
Tunggu.

602
00:37:23,397 --> 00:37:25,066
Tunggu. Eun-ho!

603
00:37:25,524 --> 00:37:26,442
Sayang!

604
00:37:26,525 --> 00:37:27,777
TUTUP CEPAT
MOHON MAAF

605
00:37:27,860 --> 00:37:29,153
