606
00:37:32,031 --> 00:37:34,116
Dia tahu aku berselingkuh.

607
00:37:34,950 --> 00:37:36,952
Tapi kabar kehamilan itu
tetap dirahasiakan.

608
00:37:38,287 --> 00:37:39,413
Lalu kami ke Kanada.

609
00:37:39,914 --> 00:37:41,874
Harus kuceritakan semuanya?

610
00:37:41,957 --> 00:37:46,462
