628
00:38:43,102 --> 00:38:46,021
Kami sudah kelompokkan detailnya
saat bercerai.

629
00:38:46,105 --> 00:38:48,274
Kirim uangnya jika tak mau
melihatku tiap hari.

630
00:38:50,526 --> 00:38:51,777
Haruskah aku datang tiap hari?

631
00:38:51,861 --> 00:38:53,112
- Besok juga?
- Berapa?

632
00:38:53,195 --> 00:38:55,406
