677
00:42:48,097 --> 00:42:49,223
Kau bahkan minum soju

678
00:42:49,306 --> 00:42:50,641
di hari pertama kita bertemu.

679
00:42:52,559 --> 00:42:54,061
Nona Daun Bawang dan Pak Payung.

