709
00:44:24,943 --> 00:44:26,778
Aku makan <i>ramyeon</i> di rumahnya.

710
00:44:27,362 --> 00:44:28,697
Apa? Dia pria?

711
00:44:29,281 --> 00:44:31,325
Kau ke rumah pria
yang tak begitu kau kenal?

712
00:44:31,408 --> 00:44:32,743
